<h3>How can i modify templates files?</h3>
<div>
<p>
Templates files you can find in "templates/front_templates" folder. It's consist of main and item. You can look at already exist files and create you own. Just don't forget to apply their in the list in "Apply Templates" tab.
</p>
</div>

<h3>Can i place two lists with the same project on one page?</h3>
<div>
<p>
Unfoturnately, No. You need to create separately projects. It's because in templates uses class ids for main container and item container (it's need to flexible setup templates files).
</p>
